cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: QDebrisFlow
abstract: >-
  QGIS plugin that models post-fire debris flows based on the quadratic
  rheological model of O'Brien and Julien (1985, 1988) and the local inertial
  approximation of the shallow water equations (LIA). Based on the FLO-2D
  formulation. Outputs: maximum depth envelope (h_max), maximum velocity
  (V_max), final deposit (h_final), flow arrival time map.
type: software
